Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.59,0:01:44.74,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}I've been ignoring everyone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.74,0:01:47.04,EN-op,,0,0,0,,I've been wandering around
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.04,0:01:51.44,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}I've been deceived everything. At that time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.80,0:01:56.49,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Then you appeared in front of me. You ignited my pale heart
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.51,0:02:00.79,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}We've been looking for each other from now on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.00,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Save you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.15,0:02:07.59,JP-op,,0,0,0,,際限ない犠牲を
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.07,0:02:12.97,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}朦朧とした理想を
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.74,0:02:16.72,JP-op,,0,0,0,,もう無駄にしないようにと
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.72,0:02:21.34,JP-op,,0,0,0,,悲しみを切り刻んだ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.04,0:02:24.36,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.36,0:02:27.59,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.61,0:02:31.78,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Just now. Chip at your heart. We just fight for freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.91,0:02:36.49,JP-op,,0,0,0,,奪い合って　汚し合って
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.49,0:02:40.68,JP-op,,0,0,0,,それでも守りたくて
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.85,0:02:43.08,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.08,0:02:46.54,EN-op,,0,0,0,,Get away from dark nightmare
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.55,0:02:51.05,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}We don't want to go through that again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.05,0:02:56.62,JP-op,,0,0,0,,{\an1}時は満ちた　始まりの鐘が鳴る
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.58,0:03:03.65,EN-op,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}Get away from me
